---
---

<section
  class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-6 transition-colors"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl text-center overflow-visible">

    <!-- Rol -->
    <span
      class="
        inline-flex items-center
        mb-6
        px-4 py-1.5
        rounded-full
        text-sm font-medium
        bg-blue-100 text-blue-700
        dark:bg-blue-900/30 dark:text-blue-300
      "
    >
      Full Stack Engineer · DevOps
    </span>

    <!-- Heading -->
    <h1
      class="
        text-5xl md:text-6xl
        font-bold
        mb-8
        tracking-tight
        leading-[1.35]
        overflow-visible
        text-gray-900 dark:text-white
      "
    >
      Hola, soy
      <span
        class="
          block
          mt-4
          pb-3
          leading-[1.35]
          overflow-visible
          bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600
          bg-clip-text text-transparent
          relative
        "
      >
        Javier Rojas Castro
        <span class="absolute inset-x-0 -bottom-2 h-2"></span>
      </span>
    </h1>




    <!-- Descripción -->
    <p
      class="
        text-lg md:text-xl
        text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400
        mb-10
        max-w-2xl
        mx-auto
        leading-relaxed
      "
    >
      Ingeniero de software con fuerte enfoque en
      <span class="font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">backend</span> y
      <span class="font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">APIs REST escalables</span>.
      Experiencia construyendo soluciones empresariales con
      <span class="font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">.NET</span>,
      <span class="font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">SQL Server</span> y
      entornos
      <span class="font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Linux / Windows Server</span>,
      complementado con frontend moderno en
      <span class="font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">React</span>,
      <span class="font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Astro</span>,
      <span class="font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">TypeScript</span> y
      <span class="font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Tailwind CSS</span>.
    </p>



    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
      <a
        href="/#projects"
        class="
          inline-flex items-center justify-center
          px-8 py-3
          rounded-lg
          bg-blue-600 text-white
          hover:bg-blue-700
          dark:bg-blue-500 dark:hover:bg-blue-600
          transition
          font-semibold
          shadow-lg
        "
      >
        Ver Proyectos
      </a>

      <a
        href="/#contact"
        class="
          inline-flex items-center justify-center
          px-8 py-3
          rounded-lg
          border border-gray-300 dark:border-neutral-700
          bg-white/70 dark:bg-neutral-800/70
          text-gray-900 dark:text-white
          hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-neutral-700
          transition
          font-semibold
          backdrop-blur
        "
      >
        Contacto
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
